msgid ""
"Before using a Redis cache with Laravel, you will need to either install the "
"PhpRedis PHP extension via PECL or install the `predis/predis` package "
"(~1.0) via Composer. [Laravel Sail](/docs/{{version}}/sail) already includes "
"this extension. In addition, official Laravel deployment platforms such as "
"[Laravel Forge](https://forge.laravel.com) and [Laravel Vapor](https://vapor."
"laravel.com) have the PhpRedis extension installed by default."
msgstr ""
"在 Laravel 內使用 Redis 快取前，必須先通過 PECL 安裝 PhpRedis PHP 擴充套件，"
"或是通過 Composer 安裝 `predis/predis` 套件（~1.0）。[Laravel Sail](/docs/"
"{{version}}/sail) 已內建了該擴充套件。此外，官方的 Laravel 部署平台，如 "
"[Laravel Forge](https://forge.laravel.com) 與 [Laravel Vapor](https://vapor."
"laravel.com) 都已預設安裝了 PhpRedis 擴充套件。"

